name: Address Color Hash
description:
Enter a Tezos address into the text box in the bottom left of the window. This address will be hashed with SHA256. This 64 character hash is then broken up into ten separate strings of six characters. These six character strings are used as hex color codes, and are displayed on the screen. The unique SHA hash is displayed at the top of the window.

Wallet information fetched from tzkt.io api
